<odoo>
    <data>
        <template id="l10n_ro_stock_picking_report.report_tally">

            <t t-call="web.html_container">
                <t t-foreach="docs.filtered(lambda record: record.picking_type_code == 'incoming')" t-as="o">
                    <t t-call="web.internal_layout">
                        <div class="page">
                            <div class="col-xs-3">
                                <span t-field="o.company_id.name"/><br/>
                                <span t-field="o.company_id.vat"/>
                                <span t-field="o.company_id.partner_id.nrc"/><br/>
                                <span t-field="o.company_id.street"/>
                                <span t-field="o.company_id.city"/>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-xs-6">
                                <h3>Borderou de achiziție</h3>
                                <h4>nr. <span t-field="o.name"/><span> Data: </span><span t-field="o.date"/></h4>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-xs-3"></div>
                            <table class="table table-condensed table-bordered">
                                <thead>
                                    <tr>
                                        <th class="text-center">Nr.</th>
                                        <th class="text-center">Numele și prenumele</th>
                                        <th class="text-center">Domiciliul</th>
                                        <th class="text-center">Serie/Nr. CI</th>
                                        <th class="text-center">Denumirea produselor</th>
                                        <th class="text-center">Cantitate</th>
                                        <th class="text-center">Preț unitar</th>
                                        <th class="text-center">Suma plătită</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    <t t-set="total" t-value="0"/>
                                    <t t-set="nr_crt" t-value="1"/>
                                   <tr t-foreach="o.move_lines" t-as="move">
                                        <t t-set="line" t-value="get_line(move)"/>
                                        <td>
                                            <span t-esc="nr_crt"/>
                                        </td>
                                        <td>
                                            <span t-field="o.partner_id.name"/>
                                        </td>
                                        <td>
                                            <span t-field="o.partner_id.street"/>
                                        </td>
                                       <td><span t-field="o.partner_id.id_nr"/></td>
                                       <td><span t-field="move.product_id"/></td>
                                       <td><span t-field="move.product_uom_qty"/><span t-field="move.product_uom" groups="uom.group_uom"/></td>
                                       <td><span t-esc="formatLang(line['price'])"/></td>
                                       <td><span t-esc="formatLang(move.product_uom_qty*line['price'])"/> </td>
                                       <t t-set="nr_crt" t-value="nr_crt+1"/>
                                       <t t-set="total" t-value="total+move.product_uom_qty*line['price']"/>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td colspan="7" style="text-align:center;">Total: </td>
                                        <td><span t-esc="formatLang(total)"/></td>
                                    </tr>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-sm-12">
                                    <h4>CONSIMȚĂMÂNT - ACORD PENTRU PRELUCRAREA DATELOR CU CARACTER PERSONAL</h4>
                                <p>Prin semnarea prezentului document mi-am exprimat acordul expres cu privire la prelucrarea datelor mele cu caracter personal de catre <span t-field="o.company_id"/>. Am fost informat ca beneficiezde dreptul de acces la datele mele cu caracter personal, dreptul de intervenție și de opoziție justificativă la prelucrarea acestora de a nu fi supus unei decizii individuale și de a mă adresa justiției, în condițiile specificate de art. 13-18 în legea nr.677/2001.</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-sm-4 pull-left">
                                    <h4>DATA <span t-field="o.date" t-field-options='{"format": "dd MM yyyy"}'/>    </h4>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-sm-4 pull-right">
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-sm-4 pull-left">
                                    <h4>SEMNĂTURA</h4>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!--<p>&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;&#45;</p>-->
